latestPosts.caption:
Last year was a rollercoaster ride of emotions, with ups and downs that tested my strength and faith. There were moments when it felt like the darkness would consume me, but in those hard times, I found peace in Sai Baba's divine presence. No one knows what I went through, but He does, and His guidance helped me navigate through the toughest of times. Whenever I think of Him, tears fill my eyes, and I am reminded of the power of faith and trust. I'm not posting this to seek validation, but to acknowledge the blessings I have received. Sai Baba's love and compassion have been my guiding light, and I'm grateful for His presence in my life. 🙏❤️
